"Например, \"Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketPhone###DynamicField\"."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:720
msgid ""
"If the setting is empty or does not have the required dynamic field name, "
"click on the \"+\" button to add a new entry. For example Key: Field1, "
"Content: 1."
msgstr ""
"Если параметр пустой или не содержит требуемого имени динамического поля, "
"нажмите кнопку \"+\"  и добавьте необходимую пару значений. Например, Ключ: "
"Поле1, Содержание: 1."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/dynamicfields-configuration.xml:724
msgid ""
"If the setting already has the dynamic field name listed be sure that is set "
"to \"1\" to display the field or to \"2\" to display it as mandatory."
msgstr ""
